            <content:encoded><![CDATA[https://www.gamespot.com/articles/path-of-exile-2-guides-hub/1100-6528305/?ftag=CAD-01-10abi2f<br/><br/><div id="readability-page-1" class="page"><p>
    <span data-nosnippet="">GameSpot may receive revenue from affiliate and advertising partnerships for sharing this content and from purchases through links.</span>
  </p><article itemscope="" data-type-id="1100" data-guid="1100-6528305">

            
            
  


        

  


        
        
              <section>

                  
          <div data-content-element-selector="p, .js-buylink-item-container" data-allowed-classes-selector="js-buylink-item-container">
                <p><a href="https://www.gamespot.com/games/path-of-exile-2/" data-ref-id="5000-504817">Path of Exile 2</a> is finally out in early access and while only <a href="https://www.gamespot.com/gallery/path-of-exile-2-release-date-early-access-and-eveything-we-know/2900-5988/" data-ref-id="2900-5988">half of the eventual content</a> is in the game right now, there are still hours of playtime available. Players can progress through three campaign Acts, dozens of varied and challenging bosses, six distinct classes, and plenty of different gear iterations.</p><p>While you can choose to carve out your own path in Path of Exile 2, there's no harm in taking a look at some guides for help along the way. That's where we come in, and you can check out every guide we've done so far in Path of Exile 2 below.</p><div data-embed-type="toc"><p><span><strong>Table of Contents</strong> [<a data-toggle="collapse" href="#toc_list">hide</a>]</span></p><ul id="toc_list"><li><a href="#Path_of_Exile_2_guides_hub">Path of Exile 2 guides hub</a><ul><li><a href="#Starter_guides">Starter guides</a></li><li><a href="#Quest_guides">Quest guides</a></li><li><a href="#Boss_fights">Boss fights</a></li><li><a href="#Build_guides">Build guides</a></li></ul></li></ul></div><h2 id="Path_of_Exile_2_guides_hub">Path of Exile 2 guides hub</h2><p>We have divided our guides hub into various categories so you can scroll through to easily find whatever you're searching for. Whether it be a tough boss fight or a build guide, we'll have a guide on it in the coming days and weeks following the early access release of Path of Exile 2. More guides will be added to the hub as new content comes to the ARPG as well.</p><h3 id="Starter_guides">Starter guides</h3><p>If you're just starting out in Path of Exile 2 or are perhaps new to ARPGs as a whole, this is the section you'll want to pay attention to initially. These guides go over basic mechanics, settings, and other content you'll find at the start of the game.</p><ul><li><a href="https://www.gamespot.com/articles/path-of-exile-2-cross-play-explained/1100-6527844/" data-ref-id="1100-6527844">Cross-Play And Cross-Save Explained</a></li><li><a href="https://www.gamespot.com/gallery/path-of-exile-2-release-date-early-access-and-eveything-we-know/2900-5988/" data-ref-id="2900-5988">Release Date, Early Access, And Eveything We Know</a></li><li><a href="https://www.gamespot.com/articles/path-of-exile-2-best-pc-settings-to-use/1100-6528244/" data-ref-id="1100-6528244">Best PC Settings To Use</a></li><li><a href="https://www.gamespot.com/articles/path-of-exile-2-how-to-get-uncut-skill-gems/1100-6528278/" data-ref-id="1100-6528278">How To Get Uncut Skill Gems</a></li><li><a href="https://www.gamespot.com/articles/path-of-exile-2-how-to-upgrade-healing-and-mana-flasks/1100-6528241/" data-ref-id="1100-6528241">How To Upgrade Healing And Mana Flasks</a></li><li><a href="https://www.gamespot.com/articles/path-of-exile-2-how-to-identify-items-for-free/1100-6528299/" data-ref-id="1100-6528299">How To Identify Items For Free</a></li><li><a href="https://www.gamespot.com/articles/path-of-exile-2-how-to-respec-passive-skills/1100-6528300/" data-ref-id="1100-6528300">How To Respec Passive Skills</a></li></ul><h3 id="Quest_guides">Quest guides</h3><p>Stuck on a certain quest? Maybe you're not sure how to progress or how to find the next zone to proceed with your current objective. Either way, if you need help with any quest-related goal, check out these guides.</p><ul><li><a href="https://www.gamespot.com/articles/path-of-exile-2-how-to-unlock-the-salvage-bench-and-salvage-items/1100-6528296/" data-ref-id="1100-6528296">How To Unlock The Salvage Bench And Salvage Items</a></li><li><a href="https://www.gamespot.com/articles/path-of-exile-2-how-to-find-the-entrance-to-the-village-in-trail-of-corruption/1100-6528291/" data-ref-id="1100-6528291">How To Get Into The Village In Trail Of Corruption</a></li><li><a href="https://www.gamespot.com/articles/path-of-exile-2-how-to-open-the-memorial-gate-in-the-cemetery/1100-6528274/" data-ref-id="1100-6528274">How To Open The Memorial Gate In The Cemetery</a></li></ul><h3 id="Boss_fights">Boss fights</h3><p>Path of Exile 2 features some extremely tough boss fights. While some are easier than others, a few bosses make you scratch your head and wonder how in the world you're going to get past it. To make your life simpler, we've broken down some of the harder bosses in the game and given you the best strategies to defeat them.</p><ul><li><a href="https://www.gamespot.com/articles/path-of-exile-2-how-to-beat-the-executioner/1100-6528287/" data-ref-id="1100-6528287">How To Beat The Executioner</a></li></ul><h3 id="Build_guides">Build guides</h3><p>Finally, if you're playing a certain class, you'll likely have some questions about what skills to use or what to spend your passive ability points on. That's where the build guides come in, giving a starting path on the best ways to play your chosen class in Path of Exile 2.</p><p>That wraps up all the guides we've done in Path of Exile 2. As we previously mentioned, more guides are being added to this hub frequently, so check back soon if you don't see the guide you need.</p>
  
                        
    
        
        
  
